            <thetext>For Android ICS there is a fix of the double drawed input field problem:


// Android ICS Fix for Input fields.
input[type=&quot;text&quot;]:not(.selectbox), input[type=&quot;number&quot;], input[type=&quot;password&quot;] {
  -webkit-user-modify: read-write-plaintext-only;
  -webkit-tap-highlight-color:rgba(0,0,0,0);
  outline-style: none;
}

This fix works for Android Ice Cream Sandwich versions (4.0-4.0.4).
It should be used in qooxdoo Mobile, too.</thetext>
